  "title": "Update the infinite hits guide to use the connector.",
  "body": "**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\nThe [guide in the doc](https://www.algolia.com/doc/tutorials/search-ui/instant-search/infinite-scroll/instantsearchjs/) is implemented as a custom widget.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\nIt should be implemented using the connector because:\r\n - the connector hides part of the complexity, using it would make it easier to grasp\r\n - we want to promote connectors over custom widgets when possible\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nThe `render` can be tricky as it is triggered both when the search comes back or the search is considered stalled.\r\n",
